metadata.name: Kek Kicks
metadata.description:
On the tongue of these Dank Sneeks, you’ll find a shout out to the homie Erick Calderon (Snowfro) and his Chromie Squiggles.

Squiggles are a project that almost single handedly lit the candle for generative art, teaching us all how incredibly well traits and iterations within a generative art collection could present themselves, and even sport, as they’re even featured IRL, on the shirts of Crawley Town FC.

Shout out Squiggles & Snowfro.

Second up, as we make our way down the kick, you’ll see an easily recognisable pair of shades… to those who know. These belong to one XCOPY, a meme lord amongst meme plebs, having been created for the memes.

Shout out XCOPY.

Next you’ve got a classic “GM”, you know we love one or two of those with our cobbee’s…

Then the face of pepe, our resilient frog.
